description:
Riding the Balkans

Travel Documentary hosted by Henry Cole, published by Travel Channel UK broadcasted as part of TC World's Greatest Motorcycle Rides series in 2015 - English narration. 
http://docuwiki.net/images/7/79/Riding-the-Balkans-Cover.jpg

Information
------------------------------
A 2000km ride through Slovenia, Croatia, Bosnia and Herzegovina, Serbia and Bulgaria which is historically rich with stunning scenery and roads, diverse cultures and great people certainly has the hallmarks of a World's greatest motorcycle ride.
